Linnaeus, 1758
</taxonomicName>
], by subsequent monotypy (
<bibRefCitation author="Weber, F." box="[158,299,1804,1829]" pageId="1" pageNumber="74" refId="ref5648" refString="Weber, F. (1795) Nomenclator entomologicus. C. E. Bohn, Chilonii et Hamburgii [= Kiel &amp; Hamburg], 171 pp." type="book" year="1795">Weber 1795</bibRefCitation>
